    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kite Hunter is an action Shooter game with a first person view. As a player you are hunting  kites, paper planes and other flying objects using weapons like catapult, Nurf-gun etc. Different kites have different flying patterns and also different hit points.  The game supports both game controller and keyboard for shooting kites.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188350/extras/faa09a48ddae2853e83e09cab0be4a4f.poster.avif?t=1753337140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188350/extras/faa09a48ddae2853e83e09cab0be4a4f.webm?t=1753337140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188350/extras/faa09a48ddae2853e83e09cab0be4a4f.mp4?t=1753337140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Boss Kites:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the end of every environment, there is a boss kite or a flying object which needs high amount of hits to finish. Each of these kites also hold unique puzzle elements  and need a strategy for a hunt down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188350/extras/770a4dd6d6f63517c44152d9b6381714.poster.avif?t=1753337140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188350/extras/770a4dd6d6f63517c44152d9b6381714.webm?t=1753337140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188350/extras/770a4dd6d6f63517c44152d9b6381714.mp4?t=1753337140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Special Weapons:</strong><br>Special weapons can attained by hitting  balloons or can be purchased from market place. Both weather and the place of hunting impacts how easy or difficult it is to shoot down kites.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188350/extras/8c1d356bf03257665711855aac59a589.poster.avif?t=1753337140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188350/extras/8c1d356bf03257665711855aac59a589.webm?t=1753337140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188350/extras/8c1d356bf03257665711855aac59a589.mp4?t=1753337140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Environment:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The environment hides relics, Aim at different objects in landscape using slingshot to find out hidden relics that can be used in market place for buying or upgrading weapons. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188350/extras/902ccef882079632103f9cd7b0725e77.avif?t=1753337140\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Toys Shop:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Relics collected during levels can be used to buy weapons from the Toy Shop.  The weapons once purchased  cannot be returned or resold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Features:</strong><br>Single Player<br>Boss Kites<br>Market Place<br>4 Different Environments<br>8 Different Weapons<br>Realistic Physics</p>",
